name: Dark Morphs : Kleroids
description:
These pesky little kleroids(dont google it up, i discovered these first and named them ) a group of Genetically enhanced mutant life form, that could stick to any surface and clone itself untill it covers up the whole surface. After which, it starts eating the hell out of what it just captured. Legend has it that it is indestructible and would only perish after it consumes and fills up the entire cosmos. Hope these suckers get sucked into blackholes and die soon, I doubt these pesky ones could even eat the blackholes.
